# YENA Images Folder

Upload all your images here to replace Unsplash links.

## How to Use:
1. Upload your images to this folder (public/images/)
2. Name them descriptively (e.g., team-brian.jpg, hero-banner.jpg)
3. Reference them in code as: /images/your-image-name.jpg

## Recommended Image Sizes:
- Hero/Banner images: 1920x1080px
- Team photos: 800x800px (square)
- Blog images: 1200x630px
- Course thumbnails: 800x600px
- About page images: 1200x800px

## Supported Formats:
- JPG/JPEG (recommended for photos)
- PNG (for images with transparency)
- WebP (for better compression)

## Example Usage in Code:
```jsx
<img src="/images/team-brian.jpg" alt="Brian Bright" />
```

## Current Unsplash Links to Replace:
You can find Unsplash links in:
- src/app/about/page.tsx (team photos, impact images)
- src/app/jobs/page.tsx (job images)
- src/app/blog/page.tsx (blog images)
- src/components/HeroSlider.tsx (hero images)

Simply upload your images here and update the src attributes!
